                            "val": "Anti-Tamper (AT) Technology Support.  The Protective Technologies (PT) organization is the Army's Technical Center for the DoD AT program, which is focused on preventing exploitation reverse engineering (RE) of U.S. systems lost or captured on the battlefield or sold via Foreign Military Sales (FMS) or Direct Commercial Sales (DCS).  In support of this mission, PT's classified efforts are focused on AT Validation and Verification (V&V) activities with Army programs, AT\/RE Lab facilities and equipment and AT\/RE Lab assessments."
